title: Solve for $$t$$ in the y(t) Equation
text: Solve for $$t$$ in the y(t) equation, we have $$t=\frac{y}{2}$$.

title: Substitute $$t$$ Into the x(t) Equation
text: Substitute $$t=\frac{y}{2}$$ into the x(t) equation, we have $$x=\left(\frac{y}{2}\right)^3-\frac{y}{2}=\frac{y^3}{8}-\frac{y}{2}$$
